== Uri ==

Deng glands makadake lang bilang aduang lupung :
* [[Endocrine]] glands- deting glands a papalual de ing karelang productu keng surface imbes na keng kapamilatan ning duct.
* [[Exocrine]] glands- papalual yang productu kapamilatan ning duct, deng glands ketinglupung malyari lang mangadake keng atlung lupung:
** [[Apocrine]] glands - metung a dake ning papalual a [[cell (biology)|cell]] nig katawan nung nu mawawala kabang magpalual ya o ausan secretion. Ing  ''apocrine gland'' keraklan magagamit ya king daleraya king [[sweating|apocrine sweat glands]], dapot isipan da ing apocrine sweat glands mapalyaring e tutung apocrine glands pauli ning mekad e gagamit a apocrine a paralan para keng pamagpalual o secretion.
** [[Holocrine]] glands - deng eganaganang cell mikakawani la papra apalual do reng substances (antimo, sebaceous glands)
** [[Merocrine]] glands - debg cells a reni papalual da ing karelang  substances kapamilatan ning [[exocytosis]] (antimo, mucous at serous glands). Mayayaus ya naman  "eccrine."
Ing uri ning secretory productu ning [[Exocrine]] gland mapalyaring metung ya kareng atlung categoria:
* [[Serous]] glands- papalual yang maranum-danum, keraklan sagana ya keng [[protein]] a productu.
[[Mucous]] glands- papalual yang marayuput a productu, sagana ya keng [[carbohydrates]] (e.g., glycoproteins)
* [[Sebaceous]] glands- papalual yang  lipid a productu

